\begin_inset Formula \( f(x+k)=cz^{x+k}+ax+ak+b=\left( cz^{k}\right) z^{x}+ax+(ak+b) \)
\end_inset 

.
 It is also scale invariant since 
\begin_inset Formula \( f(kx)=c\left( z^{k}\right) ^{x}+(ak)x+b \)
\end_inset 

.
